name: black ladybird earphones
description:
These beautiful earbud headphones have a ladybird design, and are ideal from MP3/4 players, PC’s, i-phone's, hand held games consoles etc; basically anything that uses a 3.5mm headphone.

These headphones have a special sound insulating silicone earbud to help prevent outside noise from being leaked in. They come with a second pair of silicone earbuds in a different colour.

The silicone earbuds are soft and comfortable, and have a dynamic shape that fits into the ears naturally.

Each pair comes in its own see through plastic container as shown in the picture.

Great for kids AND grown-ups.

• Length: ~1.2m 
• Sensitivity: 108dB 
• Impedance: 16 ohms 
• Frequency Response: 18-23,000 Hz
• Total Weight: 38.2g 
• Plug Diameter:3.5mm
